# BEFORE PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT:
# 1. Update TEST_DB_DATABASE to production database name (CSP_345844_BurkhartPeterson)
# 2. Test thoroughly before deploying
# 3. Enable write operations: PRACTICECS_WRITE_ENABLED=true
# 4. Monitor all operations closely

# Production Database Connection (NOT CURRENTLY USED - for future reference)
